  "10 liters": "",
  "Let u = sin(t), du = cos(t) dt. When t = 0, u = 0; when t = pi/2, u = 1. Integral = 10 * integral from 0 to 1 of u^2 du = 10[u^3/3] from 0 to 1 = 10/3 liters.": "",
  "A spring exerts a force of F(x) = 8x * e^(x^2) newtons at displacement x meters. Using u-substitution, find the work done from x = 0 to x = 1.": "",
