  "Work = integral from 0 to 1 of 8x e^(x^2) dx. Let u = x^2, du = 2x dx. When x = 0, u = 0; when x = 1, u = 1. W = 4 integral from 0 to 1 of e^u du = 4[e^u] from 0 to 1 = 4(e - 1) joules.": "",
  "Bacteria in a culture grow at a rate of B'(t) = 500/(1 + 2t) bacteria per hour. Using u-substitution, how many bacteria are produced between t = 0 and t = 4 hours?": "",
  "250 ln(4) bacteria": "",
  "250 ln(9) bacteria": "",
  "500 ln(4) bacteria": "",
  "500 ln(9) bacteria": "",
  "Let u = 1 + 2t, du = 2 dt. When t = 0, u = 1; when t = 4, u = 9. Integral = (500/2) integral from 1 to 9 of du/u = 250[ln|u|] from 1 to 9 = 250(ln 9 - ln 1) = 250 ln(9).": "",
  "An electric current charges a capacitor at a rate of Q'(t) = 6t^2/(t^3 + 8) coulombs per second. Using u-substitution, find the charge accumulated from t = 0 to t = 2 seconds.": "",
  "2 ln(2) coulombs": "",
  "3 ln(2) coulombs": "",
  "6 ln(2) coulombs": "",
  "ln(2) coulombs": "",
  "Let u = t^3 + 8, du = 3t^2 dt. When t = 0, u = 8; when t = 2, u = 16. Integral = (6/3) integral from 8 to 16 of du/u = 2[ln|u|] from 8 to 16 = 2(ln 16 - ln 8) = 2 ln(16/8) = 2 ln(2) coulombs.": ""
